lead_paragraph: Tokyo Sexwale's bid to become FIFA president was doomed as soon as his own confederation refused to back him, South African Football Association head Danny Jordaan said of his compatriot's failed attempt to lead soccer's governing body.

headline.print_headline: Jordaan Blames CAF for Sexwale FIFA Failure
headline.main: Jordaan Blames CAF for Sexwale FIFA Failure
